        h2 Custom Icon Set

        p Animatik's mix of stickers, filters, and graphic text made it difficult to find an existing icon set that felt cohesive while still including icons that described the app's odd medly of features.

        p At the same time, the total number of icons was relatively small, so a custom set was reasonable and in-budget.

        p Strong information architexture early on is what made this set possible. Every user interaction was mapped out and described in detail before any icons had to be created, allowing me to have a feel for the overall vibe of the interaction set from the start, and avoiding any unpleasant and hard-to-integrate surprise additions down the road.

